name: Broken waveform #2, 2019
description: While printing work for a solo show, the paper started rejecting dyes, which pooled and re-pixellated the image. This was one of my first 'failed prints'. Originating image is a handheld zoom at dusk on rising ocean swell. | 	 	Minted 22  - 10 + 2 'artist proofs' | 	Secondary royalties: 10%. Half to an environmental charity of my choosing.
